<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM6.3.8">
<l>muḷintīn tavēṅkaṭattu mūrippe ruṅkaḷiṟṟāl</l>
<l>viḷintīn tamāmarampōl vīḻntārai niṉaiyātē</l>
<l>yaḷintōrn tacintainiṉ pālaṭiyēṟk kuvāṉulakam</l>
<l>teḷintē yeṉṟeytuvatu tiruviṇṇa karāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For me, [your] servant, whose thoughts contemplate and cling to you,</l>
<l>Not envying those who fell like huge trees which are scorched and dead,</l>
<l>[Pushed over] by great bull elephants in the hot wilderness</l>
<l rend="indent">which is scorched and parched,</l>
<l>When will the heavenly world, revealing [itself], be attainable,</l>
<l rend="indent">[Lord] of Tiruviṇṇakar?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
